Contributions
-------------

Synthesizer images and help texts are provided by Nick Copeland:
http://bristol.sourceforge.net

Installing
----------

Run:

./autogen
./configure
./make 
./make install

Now start with bristolgui

Current Version
---------------

The current version is v0.1, which means it's a prototype. There is no
Makefile yet, but if you have installed the GTK+ dev libraries you 
should be able to import the head branch into eclipse/CDT and compile. 

